%% * (1) Top

%% ** (2) Building the package

LDF 2012.07.05.
LDF 2013.05.30.

   libtoolize
   aclocal 
   autoconf
   autoheader 
   automake --add-missing --copy 
   configure --prefix=`pwd` 
   make 
   make install

Notes:

automake:   The options `--add-missing' and `--copy' only need to be used the first time.

configure:  If the `--prefix' argument isn't used, the `install' target of `make' tries
            to install the executable files under `/usr/local/bin/'.  A directory other than the 
            current directory may be used.  The argument must be an absolute path.


